{
  "name": "Breath of Dust Instability",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Bukijutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>(You cannot score a critical hit with this jutsu) You begin to collect and manifest earth release chakra until it laces the striking portion of your weapon. The earth release chakra begins to magnify the weight and striking power of your attacks allowing you blow  through anything in your path with little difficulty. You fire multiple shots in an attempt to strike multiple angles at once.</p><p>Make a single ranged taijutsu attack against one creature you can see within range. On a hit, you deal your weapons damage die + 2d4 earth damage, you do not add your ability modifier to damage.</p><p>If your first is 5 or higher than the AC of your target, make a second melee taijutsu attack against the same creature, dealing 3d6 earth damage and inflicting the bruised condition.</p><p>If the second attack is 5 or higher than the AC of your target, make a third attack against the same creature, dealing 3d6 earth damage and inflicting the bruised condition.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 1d6. If this jutsu is cast at S-Rank, the earth damage increases by 1 step, to a  d8.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
